{"tid":2497990,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"熱血公民政黨民望評分則創2017年以來新低！繼續排榜尾！","createTime":"2021-04-21T00:52:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T09:41:25.000Z","uid":7439,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"75cf1c52a46454558dd39b24e5cd75c7279f9a02","tid":2497990,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T00:52:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdYsqf59NqVQ72vvvue2ByHMzF145hxWBaCoWsF2WdvAs?filename=FBprcM6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFBprcM6.png&h=98224f7e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPb5BHrMQJFWtbPUZgQmb8AhkeMaKirTqcSSeRFRmJkhV?filename=8Ur9ayN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Ur9ayN.png&h=616dc2cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a93f3adb7b36fcc1373bc129c8b1c01436b46d7f","tid":2497990,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T00:53:33.000Z","msg":"最新調查顯示，市民對政治團體的最新支持度排名，<span class=\"red\">首位是民陣，得 40.2 分</span>;民主黨、公民 黨、人民力量、民建聯和自由黨，分別得 38.8、38.2、38.2、35.4 及 35.0 分;社民連、工聯會、 新民黨和熱血公民分別排第七至十位，得 34.6、33.0、29.7 及 28.7 分。相比六個月前，民主黨、人民力 量、社民連和熱血公民的評分顯著下跌，而民建聯、工聯會及經民聯的評分則顯著上升。<span class=\"red\">民陣、 民主黨、公民黨和民協的評分是其分別於 2005、1994、2006 和 1991 年首次被評分以來新低。 社民連和熱血公民評分則創 2017 年以來新低。</span>"},{"pid":"9679a140e02f55141001088f84e87302b77a72b7","tid":2497990,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T00:53:44.000Z","msg":"在最新調查中，民協和 經民聯分別得 36.8 及 29.3 分，但由於認知率較低而被剔除。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f398eff4c828438f8077ba8f857e34c83569facb","tid":2497990,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T00:54:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/wp-c